Q1) LIST THE CUSTOMERS KEPT ORDERS MORE THAN 100 PRODUCTS.
RESULT:
PAGE:3
EXPLANATION:
FIRST I HAD RETRIVED QUANTITY OF ORDERS FROM ORDERDETAILS TABLE AND MENTIONED

FOR GETTING THE ATTRIBUTE CUSTOMERNUMBER NEXT TO GET SUM OFTHE ORDERS KEPT
BY CUSTOMERS REPEATEDLY OR SINGLE ORDER , I HAD USED AGGREGATE FUNCTION
SUM().

CLAUSE.I HAD CONCLUDED THE COMPLETE SENARIO IN COMMON TABLE EXPESSION
NAMED A AND JOINED TABLE A WITH CUSTOMERS TO GET ATTRIBUTE CUSTOMER NAME.
